This is what steam does.

*Instructions*

1. Download the Webex – Cisco Webex Meetings App and login half an hour before. Click on the link for the Webex meeting sent to your mail to join the meeting.
 
2. Make sure you name your phone / WEBEX Application in your name so that we will be able to see your name instead of iPhone, redmi or any other name during Webex transmission.
 
 3. Write using black ballpoint pen and make sure you write your name, Roll Number and email ID on all the sheets and also the sheet number
 
 4. The camera should focus on both the writing and your face. If found anything suspect, it will be considered as Malpractice.
 
 5. Make sure you are seated in an isolated place and no disturbance should be there from anyone during the conduct of exam.
 
 6. Questions will be dictated by the faculty and same will also appear in chatbox of Webex App.

Instructions

1. Download the Webex – Cisco Webex Meetings App and login half an hour before. Click on the link for the Webex meeting sent to your mail to join the meeting.
 
2. Make sure you name your phone / WEBEX Application in your name so that we will be able to see your name instead of iPhone, redmi or any other name during Webex transmission.
 
 3. Write using black ballpoint pen and make sure you write your name, Roll Number and email ID on all the sheets and also the sheet number
 
 4. The camera should focus on both the writing and your face. If found anything suspect, it will be considered as Malpractice.
 
 5. Make sure you are seated in an isolated place and no disturbance should be there from anyone during the conduct of exam.
 
 6. Questions will be dictated by the faculty and same will also appear in chatbox of Webex App.

*Scanning of Answer Sheets*

*11:30 am to 11:50 AM* - Scanning of answer sheets using Microsoft Lens or any other scanner app with good quality and sending the same by single PDF file by email to *rmc.physiology@ramaiahgroup.org* with their Name, Roll Number and Email ID. Email received after 11:50 AM will not be entertained

*Instructions*

1. Download the Webex – Cisco Webex Meetings App and login half an hour before. Click on the link for the Webex meeting sent to your mail to join the meeting.
 
2. Make sure you name your phone / WEBEX Application in your name so that we will be able to see your Roll Number (pattern three digit number 001, 011) with name instead of iPhone, redmi or any other name during Webex transmission. (First your Roll Number and then your name should be displayed)
 
 3. Write using black ballpoint pen and make sure you write your name, Roll Number and email ID on all the sheets and also the sheet number
 
 4. The camera should focus on both the writing and your face. If found anything suspect, it will be considered as Malpractice.
 
 5. Make sure you are seated in an isolated place and no disturbance should be there from anyone during the conduct of exam.
 
 6. Questions will be dictated by the faculty and same will also appear in chatbox of Webex App.

Instructions

1. Download the Webex – Cisco Webex Meetings App and login half an hour before. Click on the link for the Webex meeting sent to your mail to join the meeting.
 
2. Make sure you name your phone / WEBEX Application in your name so that we will be able to see your Roll Number (pattern three digit number 001, 011) with name instead of iPhone, redmi or any other name during Webex transmission. (First your Roll Number and then your name should be displayed)
 
 3. Write using black ballpoint pen and make sure you write your name, Roll Number and email ID on all the sheets and also the sheet number
 
 4. The camera should focus on both the writing and your face. If found anything suspect, it will be considered as Malpractice.
 
 5. Make sure you are seated in an isolated place and no disturbance should be there from anyone during the conduct of exam.
 
 6. Questions will be dictated by the faculty and same will also appear in chatbox of Webex App.
